# ONPURPOSE MARKETPLACE - DEVELOPER HANDOFF PACKAGE

## 📋 QUICK START GUIDE

### 1. Clone & Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/fanaticdigitalmarketing-lab/onpurpose-marketplace.git
cd onpurpose-marketplace
npm install
```

### 2. Environment Setup
```bash
# Copy environment files
cp .env.example .env
cp .env.production.example .env.production

# Edit with your values
# DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET, CORS_ORIGIN, etc.
```

### 3. Database Setup
```bash
# Run database seeding
npm run seed

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

### 4. Deployment
- **Backend**: Deploy to Railway with PostgreSQL
- **Frontend**: Deploy to Netlify
- **Domain**: Configure custom domain

